---
import Page from "@/layouts/Page.astro";
import Prose from "@/components/starwind/prose/Prose.astro";
---

<Page
  title="About"
  description="Find Coloring Pages is a free library of printable coloring pages designed to actually be useful — simple enough for kids, clean enough to print well."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
    <h1 class="heading-2 mb-6">About Find Coloring Pages</h1>

    <Prose class="max-w-none">
      <p>
        Find Coloring Pages started with a simple frustration: most coloring pages online
        are either covered in fine detail that's impossible for young kids to color,
        or they're watermarked, locked behind sign-ups, or just hard to find.
      </p>

      <p>
        This site is the opposite of that. Every page here is free to download and print,
        no account required. The designs are deliberately simple — big shapes, clear outlines,
        enough white space to actually fill in with a crayon. They're made to be printed
        on a standard home printer and colored by real kids.
      </p>

      <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
      <p>
        Coloring pages organized by category — animals, holidays, dinosaurs, and more.
        Each page lists the difficulty level so you can find something age-appropriate quickly.
        We also have a <a href="/blog">blog</a> with practical tips on printing, supplies,
        and getting the most out of coloring time with kids.
      </p>

      <h2>Free to use</h2>
      <p>
        All coloring pages on this site are free for personal and classroom use.
        Download as many as you like, print them out, and share them freely.
      </p>

      <h2>New pages</h2>
      <p>
        We add new coloring pages regularly. If you'd like to know when new ones are
        available, you can subscribe at the bottom of this page — we'll send a short
        email when there's something new, nothing else.
      </p>
    </Prose>
  </div>
</Page>
